So like they had to really attracted all these sort of

11:36.000 --> 11:38.080
new school, like Yale, Harvard types,

11:38.080 --> 11:40.640
you know, with all of these like immaculate,

11:40.640 --> 11:42.960
like shirts with the little monogram on it.

11:42.960 --> 11:44.320
It was all sort of old school traders.

11:44.320 --> 11:46.080
And then suddenly they're making a ton of money.

11:46.080 --> 11:48.480
And I was just thinking,

11:48.480 --> 11:50.320
how do I get me some of this money, basically?

11:50.320 --> 11:51.520
How do I follow these guys?

