And just desperately trying to get them to tell me,

11:55.040 --> 11:55.840
like, what are you doing?

11:55.840 --> 11:56.720
How are you making this money?

11:56.720 --> 11:58.400
You're like, what's happening?

11:58.400 --> 11:59.440
And I was trying to figure it out.

12:00.880 --> 12:04.080
