they, the rich have all the money and all the assets,

01:08:24.160 --> 01:08:25.840
you are not going to beat them in that game.

01:08:25.840 --> 01:08:30.400
The only power you have, the only power you have is that there's more of you.

01:08:30.960 --> 01:08:33.840
And if you try and use that by trading crypto,

01:08:33.840 --> 01:08:34.720
you don't use that power.

01:08:34.720 --> 01:08:36.320
It's like the Kung Fu movies,

01:08:36.320 --> 01:08:38.240
where 100 guys fight Bruce Lee one at a time.

