01:16:58.400 --> 01:16:59.840
Because if you turn around to me and say,

01:17:00.480 --> 01:17:03.280
there's no problem with deficits, even massive ones,

01:17:03.280 --> 01:17:04.400
why tax the rich?

01:17:04.480 --> 01:17:05.840
We just run a massive deficit.

01:17:05.840 --> 01:17:08.080
And then what you do is you politically enable

01:17:08.080 --> 01:17:10.640
things like COVID where a massive crisis

01:17:10.640 --> 01:17:14.400
led to a Â£600 billion wealth transfer to the rich.

