Actually, what they're doing is providing a license to the transfer

01:17:30.560 --> 01:17:31.760
of wealth from poor to rich.

01:17:31.760 --> 01:17:32.960
I don't want to mischaracterize them

01:17:32.960 --> 01:17:34.480
because it's a big community and different people

01:17:34.480 --> 01:17:35.280
believe different things.

01:17:35.280 --> 01:17:38.080
And I think the high priests of it,

01:17:38.080 --> 01:17:39.840
the people who are really into it,

01:17:39.840 --> 01:17:40.800
often they will say, well, actually,

01:17:40.800 --> 01:17:42.880
MMT does support taxation of the rich.

01:17:42.880 --> 01:17:45.280
The problem is the message that has cut through

01:17:45.280 --> 01:17:46.640
is deficits are not dangerous.

